WEBVTT

00:02:58.503 --> 00:03:01.546
we the youth in Togo will organize
and we will bring you down,

00:03:01.570 --> 00:03:04.918
because you have killed
over 500 of our countrymen

00:03:04.942 --> 00:03:06.742
to seize power when your father died.

00:03:06.766 --> 00:03:08.031
We have not chosen you.

00:03:08.055 --> 00:03:10.508
You are an imposter,
and we will remove you."

00:03:10.532 --> 00:03:12.783
But I was the only known face
of the movement.

00:03:12.807 --> 00:03:15.103
Why? Because I was the only stupid one.

00:03:15.127 --> 00:03:16.775
(Laughter)

00:03:17.174 --> 00:03:19.455
And the backlashes followed.

00:03:19.479 --> 00:03:21.674
My family started receiving threats.

00:03:21.698 --> 00:03:24.174
My siblings called me one morning.

00:03:24.198 --> 00:03:25.494
They said, "You know what?

00:03:25.518 --> 00:03:28.506
When they come here to kill you,
we don't want to die with you,

00:03:28.530 --> 00:03:29.699
so move out."

00:03:29.723 --> 00:03:31.623
So yes, I moved out.